cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with the problem of pedestrian detection in aerial imagery using deep learning techniques and an embedded system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and autonomous systems, which falls under the category cs.RO (Robotics). The use of deep learning algorithms and pre-trained models suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of surveillance and monitoring, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
